OL,3,CYellow cold-health alert issued for
OL,4,Cparts of the Midlands into the new year
OL,6,FThe Met Office website reads: "There
OL,7,Fis potential for significant impacts
OL,8,Facross health and social care
OL,9,Fservices, including a rise in deaths,
OL,10,Fparticularly among those aged 65 and
OL,11,Fover or with health conditions.
OL,13,F"We may also see impacts on younger
OL,14,Fage groups, a likely increase in
OL,15,Fdemand for health services, impacts on
OL,16,Fthe workforce affecting delivery of
OL,17,Fservices and challenges keeping indoor
OL,18,Ftemperatures at the recommended 18C
OL,19,Fleading to more risk to vulnerable
OL,20,Fpeople."
