OL,3,CYellow cold-health alert issued for
OL,4,Cparts of the Midlands into the new year
OL,6,FWith cold weather increasing the risk
OL,7,Fof winter illnesses circulating such
OL,8,Fas flu, residents in Walsall are being
OL,9,Fadvised to get the flu vaccination
OL,10,Ffrom their GP or nearest pharmacy.
OL,12,FOther proactive measures can help
OL,13,Fresidents stay safe and comfortable
OL,14,Fduring colder months, particularly
OL,15,Fthose who are more likely to
OL,16,Fexperience the effects of cold weather.
