OL,3,CYellow cold-health alert issued for
OL,4,Cparts of the Midlands into the new year
OL,6,FDr Nadia Inglis, Director of Public
OL,7,FHealth at Walsall Council said: "With
OL,8,Fcolder weather forecast, your
OL,9,Fwellbeing is important to us, and it
OL,10,Fis important to check in on those more
OL,11,Fvulnerable to the cold weather.
OL,13,F"This includes older people, very
OL,14,Fyoung children and people with long
OL,15,Fterm conditions, as it can have a
OL,16,Fserious impact on health.
