OL,3,CYellow cold-health alert issued for
OL,4,Cparts of the Midlands into the new year
OL,6,F"Maintaining a comfortable indoor
OL,7,Ftemperature is also important. Try and
OL,8,Fheat your home to at least 18C, and
OL,9,Ftake other measures to protect
OL,10,Fyourself such as wearing lots of
OL,11,Flayers.
OL,13,F"Getting the help you need can help
OL,14,Fyou stay well when it is cold. Warm
OL,15,Fspaces are open and welcoming to
OL,16,Fanyone across Walsall who need
OL,17,Fsomewhere to meet other people and get
OL,18,Fsupport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^OXuD@AOU
