OL,3,CYellow cold-health alert issued for
OL,4,Cparts of the Midlands into the new year
OL,6,F"We know that winter conditions can
OL,7,Faffect your health, and it is
OL,8,Fimportant to think about which service
OL,9,Fis right for you at the right time.
OL,10,FFor everyday health needs, visit the
OL,11,FNHS website, your local pharmacy, or
OL,12,Fcontact your GP for advice and ongoing
OL,13,Fcare.
OL,15,F"If you need urgent medical help, use
OL,16,FNHS 111 online or call 111 for advice
OL,17,Fand guidance to the right service. In
OL,18,Fa life-threatening emergency, always
OL,19,Fcall 999 immediately."
